OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHow loan shark, 83, scared 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpeople into paying up      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, It may be hard to imagine how an       
OL,6, 83-year-old woman could instil such    
OL,7, fear into victims of her money lending 
OL,8, scheme that they paid her tens of      
OL,9, thousand of pounds of interest on top  
OL,10, of illegal loans.                      
OL,12,FBut loan sharks like Tabitha Richardson
OL,13,F- who was told to repay more than      
OL,14,F#173,000 to six victims this week - are
OL,15,Fon the rise due to financial pressure  
OL,16,Fbeing felt by people across the UK.    
OL,18,FThere are more loan sharks than ever   
OL,19,Funder investigation, according to the  
OL,20,Fagency Stop Loan Sharks Wales which    
OL,21,Fbrought Richardson's actions to light. 
